<PageLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy — Bastrop County Conservatives"
  heading="Privacy Policy"
>
  <p>Last Updated: October 2025</p>

  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>At Bastrop County Conservatives, your privacy is critically important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines what information we collect, how it's used, and how we protect your personal data when you visit our website, subscribe to our newsletter, volunteer, or make a donation.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We only collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us, such as your name, email address, phone number, and physical address when you:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Sign up for our newsletter or action alerts</li>
    <li>Register as a volunteer</li>
    <li>Apply for membership or make a donation</li>
    <li>Contact us via our website forms</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>The information we collect is used to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Provide you with updates on local politics, events, and candidate information</li>
    <li>Process your membership and donations (payment processing is handled securely by third-party processors; we do not store full credit card information)</li>
    <li>Coordinate volunteer activities</li>
    <li>Comply with state and federal campaign finance reporting requirements (for donations over certain limits)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Text Message (SMS) Policy</h2>
  <p>By providing your telephone number, you consent to receive calls and text messages, including prerecorded messages and via automated methods. Message & data rates may apply. Message frequency may vary. Reply 'STOP' to opt-out & 'HELP' for help.</p>
  <p><strong>Mobile information will not be shared with third parties/affiliates for marketing/promotional purposes.</strong></p>

  <h2>Data Security</h2>
  <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. We will never sell, rent, or lease our membership or donor lists to third parties.</p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@bastropcc.com">info@bastropcc.com</a>.</p>
</PageLayout>
